#: src/ui.glade:132
msgid ""
"\n"
"Alas! This not an X11 session, xsnow will probably not run.\n"
"\n"
"If you want to try it anyway, set the environment variable XSNOW_FORCE_RUN, "
"eg:\n"
"\n"
"    XSNOW_FORCE_RUN=1 xsnow\n"
"\n"
"Or, you could force an X11 session, for example by tweaking /etc/gdm3/"
"daemon.conf.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Ack! Detta är inte en X11-session, xsnow kommer förmodligen inte att köras.\n"
"\n"
"Om du ändå vill prova, ställ in miljövariabeln XSNOW_FORCE_RUN, t.ex.:\n"
"\n"
"    XSNOW_FORCE_RUN=1 xsnow\n"
"\n"
"Eller så kan du tvinga fram en X11-session, till exempel genom att justera /"
"etc/gdm3/daemon. conf.\n"
"\n"

